trans-unit.source: Represents a base class for design-time tools, not derived from <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref>, that provide smart tag or designer verb capabilities.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en basisklasse for utforming verktøy, ikke er utledet fra <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref>, som gir smart koden eller designer verbet funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> class provides the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A> properties to query for the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> collections, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>klassen gir den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A>egenskapene til å spørre etter den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb>samlinger, henholdsvis.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: However, if a design-time tool author decides not to derive from this class, the DesignerCommandSet class represents an alternative base class to provide this functionality.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en utformingen verktøyet forfatteren anser ikke skal avledes fra denne klassen, representerer klassen DesignerCommandSet et alternativt basisklassen oppgi denne funksjonaliteten.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerCommandSet class contains only three members, described in the following table.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerCommandSet inneholder bare tre medlemmer som er beskrevet i følgende tabell.

trans-unit.source: |Public member|Description| |-------------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>|Returns the collection of either the smart tags or designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: | Offentlig medlem | Beskrivelse | |-------------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>| Returnerer samlingen smart koder eller designer verb som er knyttet til komponenten utformede.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation returns `null`.| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>|Gets the collection of all the smart tags associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer base implementeringen `null`. | | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>| Henter samlingen av alle smart koder som er forbundet med komponenten utformede.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>.| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>|Gets the collection of all the designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende implementeringen kaller ganske enkelt <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>. | | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>| Henter samlingen av alle designer verb som er forbundet med komponenten utformede.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>.| A DesignerCommandSet should be added as a site-specific service.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende implementeringen kaller ganske enkelt <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>. | En DesignerCommandSet skal legges til som en tjeneste som er spesifikk for et område.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: Externally, a service of this type should first be queried to discover smart tag and designer verb functionality.
trans-unit.target: Eksternt, denne tjenestetypen må først være bedt om å oppdage smart koden og designer verbet funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: If this service is not found, then the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property should be used instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne tjenesten ikke finnes, og deretter den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen skal brukes i stedet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This procedure provides a path for backwards compatibility.
trans-unit.target: Denne prosedyren gir en bane for bakoverkompatibilitet kompatibilitet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Because this base class contains no state, the default constructor does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Siden denne basisklassen inneholder ingen tilstand, gjøre Standardkonstruktøren noe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of all the smart tags associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av alle smart koder som er forbundet med komponenten utformet.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A> with the string parameter "ActionLists".
trans-unit.target: Kaller ganske enkelt base implementeringen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>med strengparameter "ActionLists".</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> that contains the smart tags for the associated designed component.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> som inneholder smart koder for den tilknyttede utformede komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of command objects.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en samling av command-objekter.

trans-unit.source: Although the base implementation always returns `null`, the overridden version supplied by the programmer should return a collection of command objects of the type described by `name`.
trans-unit.target: Selv om base implementeringen alltid returnerer `null`, overstyrte versjonen ble levert av i programmer må returnere en samling av command-objekter av typen beskrevet av `name`.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A> properties specify the following values and meanings for this parameter.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende implementeringen av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>egenskapene angi følgende verdier og betydning for denne parameteren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: |String|Meaning| |------------|-------------| |"ActionLists"|Return a collection of all the smart tags associated with the component.| |"Verbs"|Return a collection of all the designer verbs associated with the component.|
trans-unit.target: | Streng | Det vil si | |------------|-------------| |" ActionLists "| Returnerer en samling av alle smart koder som er forbundet med komponenten. | |" Verb "| Returnerer en samling av alle designer verb som er forbundet med komponenten. |

trans-unit.source: The type of collection to return, indicating either a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> or a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Typen for samlingen skal returneres, som angir enten en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the specified type—either <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> or <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"></xref>—of command objects.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder den angitte typen, enten <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"> </xref>– for command-objekter.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer base implementeringen alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of all the designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av alle designer verb som er forbundet med komponenten utformet.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A> with the string parameter "Verbs".
trans-unit.target: Kaller ganske enkelt base implementeringen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>med strengparameter "Verb".</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"></xref> that contains the designer verbs for the associated designed component.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"> </xref> som inneholder designer verbene for den tilknyttede utformede komponenten.
